show.title: PRESIDENT MOM
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://applinks.kukufm.com/sPRARdq9qX9eN8Rr8
show.description: President Mom tells the story of a woman who returns to her hometown after years of hard work to invest in local development, only to discover her stepmother has been siphoning off the money meant for her father. Faced with betrayal and family turmoil, she launches a powerful fightback, showcasing the strength and resilience of a modern woman.
